to the editor protection of our country 's blood and treasure is the goal of our democratic leadership editorial june 23 the president 's new nuclear doctrine is harsh yet sound diplomatic rhetoric crafted to send a clear message to any country thinking about striking the united states with weapons of mass destruction or of helping any group that intends to do so if the president 's statements seem alarming the bad guys and their national sponsors will know that america is serious about protecting our way of life jeff thieret harmony pa june 23 2002 the writer is a retired air force lieutenant colonel

